name: Dystopia | Confrontation [2]
description:
When people are desperate, there are two options that can be taken:
waiting for death to come or fighting to the death.

In a dystopian world, the two choices make no difference, because sooner or later, death will inevitably come.

However, those who fighting make meaning in their own lives; 
they make the possibility in the impossible, they are a ray of hope in this almost shattered world, they are the givers of life, even though death awaits in front of their eyes.
